    "Charges were calculated by summing the numbers of glutamate and aspartate residues and lysine and arginine residues for negative and positive charges, respectively.",
    "The phmmer top 30 average score was calculated by running a phmmer search of the experimentally tested sequences against the training sequences and averaging the scores of the top 30 hits.",
    "The selected sequences had 70% and 80% identity to the closest training sequence and diverse scores on the ESM-1v metric.",
    "Round 2 pretest.",
    "CuSOD sequences were selected on the basis of the kingdom of origin (eukaryotic, viral or bacterial) and the presence of Phobius-predicted signal peptides."
